\\ & = \sum_{\color{#D61F06} n=0}^\infty \frac {(n+1)^2}{2^(n+1)} 
\\ & = \sum_{\color{#D61F06} n=0}^\infty \frac {n^2+2n+1}{2\cdot 2^n} 
\\ & = \frac 12 \sum_{\color{#D61F06} n=0}^\infty \frac {n^2}{2^n} + \frac 12{\color{#3D99F6}\sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac n{2^{n-1}}} + \frac 12 \sum_{\color{#D61F06} n=0}^\infty \frac 1{2^n} & \small \color{#3D99F6} \text{Note that } \sum_{n=1}^\infty \frac n{2^{n-1}} \text{ is sum of AGP.} 
\\ & = \frac 12 S + \frac 12 \times {\color{#3D99F6}4} + \frac 12 \left(\frac 1{1-\frac 12}\right) & \small \color{#3D99F6} \text{See note.} \\ & = \frac 12 S + 2 + 1 \\ \implies \frac 12 S & = 3 \\ S & = \boxed{6} \end{aligned} "}],"attrs":{"inline":true}},{"type":"text","text":" "}]},{"type":"text","text":"

